[SN]TITLE[SN]
Prince Charles meets Ballater flood victims at Highland Games

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Prince Charles has met Ballater residents who were hit by flooding last year, as he attended the village highland games.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Many homes and businesses were badly affected when the River Dee burst its banks in December.
It happened as Storm Frank battered Scotland.
As well as meeting with Ballater residents, the Duke of Rothesay also watched the games and met some of those taking part.
